<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="646" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="27.[2080,2674,3038,3462]" pageId="27" pageNumber="646">
The species forms a complex with 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Chaerephon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="649" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pumilus">C. pumilus</taxonomicName>
